{"tid":672242,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"若遺憾是遺憾 若故事沒說完 回頭看 梨花已落千山","createTime":"2018-05-20T22:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T03:22:47.000Z","uid":97526,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e751b0ea0460c949aaa24a3eccadc13aae5219db","tid":672242,"uid":97526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T22:04:45.000Z","msg":"我至少聽過 你說的喜歡<br />\n像涓涓溫柔途經過百川<br />\n<br />\n若遺憾遺憾 若心酸心酸<br />\n又不是非要圓滿<br />\n來年秋風亂 笑看紅葉轉<br />\n深情 只好 淺談"},{"pid":"355103acc98b6d82935c7de6f316dccb95a5e098","tid":672242,"uid":97526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T22:10:19.000Z","msg":"有些緣分是注定的<br />\n怎麼努力也沒辦法<br />\n小樹發過芽<br />\n也未必能開花<br />\n<br />\n可是你還記得嗎<br />\n那年盛夏<br />\n那個傻瓜<br />\n說的傻話<br />\n陪著你回家<br />\n陪著你長大<br />\n每天都記得打電話"},{"pid":"2bf3fffb4f32625feb0656e378771bc05cef2413","tid":672242,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T22:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e655d2ef992c6933db7bd41c8077a9b42f9a9e4","tid":672242,"uid":97526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bf3fffb4f32625feb0656e378771bc05cef2413","tid":672242,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T22:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T00:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a65ed5ac72c24e2a708f07108a29784656a04ca","tid":672242,"uid":97526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T00:47:00.000Z","msg":"可是你還記得嗎<br />\n那道晚霞<br />\n最後一次<br />\n送你回家<br />\n我沒有講話<br />\n因為怕眼淚落下"},{"pid":"beeb0ebeb57de7b4b93e66739c34d5c84fc0bf8a","tid":672242,"uid":97526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T00:47:54.000Z","msg":"我們陌生得沒有再相遇<br />\n是你給我最長久的感情<br />\n全都失去 也不差失去你"},{"pid":"af1e3d8e690dbc3f5da0d456e573ac56b3788a37","